title: Ep 9 - Your Network Determines Your Net Worth
itunes:title: Ep 9 - Your Network Determines Your Net Worth
description:
"Surround yourself with people who dream bigger than you do."
In this episode we talk about the importance of your surrounding yourself with the right people who will push and encourage you to your goals. We go over your "Top 5" and also go over the best ways to network to build up your circle of influence.
